## Safety

- All **destructive** operations (move, rename, split, structural distill, append to other notes) occur in **downstream** pipelines or skills invoked by this subagent, not in this rule body.
- This subagent only **orchestrates** (route, validate, dispatch). It does not perform backups, snapshots, or destructive MCP calls itself except as delegated to skills or pipeline rules.
- On failure: follow the Error Handling Protocol in core-guardrails and mcp-obsidian-integration; log to Errors.md and append Watcher-Result per watcher-result-append.

